OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772067788
OL,3,CHilary Benn to press Dublin on 'hugely
OL,4,Cimportant' Troubles information sharing
OL,6,FIn Belfast in January, Ms McEntee said
OL,7,Fany significant changes to legislation
OL,8,Flinked to a joint UK/Irish framework
OL,9,Fon the Troubles must have the full
OL,10,Fagreement of both governments, after
OL,11,FUK Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,12,Findicated there may be new protections
OL,13,Ffor military veterans.
OL,15,FThe joint framework on legacy unveiled
OL,16,Fby London and Dublin last September
OL,17,Foutlined a range of measures and
OL,18,Fmechanisms for dealing with historical
OL,19,Fcases from the Northern Ireland
OL,20,Fconflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772067788
OL,3,CHilary Benn to press Dublin on 'hugely
OL,4,Cimportant' Troubles information sharing
OL,6,FThe framework included commitments to
OL,7,Ffundamentally reform the structures
OL,8,Festablished by the last Conservative
OL,9,Fgovernment's contentious Legacy Act,
OL,10,Fincluding the removal of a
OL,11,Fcontroversial provision that offered a
OL,12,Fform of conditional immunity to
OL,13,Fperpetrators of Troubles crimes.
OL,15,FThe Irish Government committed to the
OL,16,F"fullest possible" co-operation with
OL,17,Fthe new legacy commission and the
OL,18,Fcreation of a dedicated legacy unit
OL,19,Fwithin the Irish police force, An
OL,20,FGarda Siochana.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@RO]
