OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772067788
OL,3,CHilary Benn to press Dublin on 'hugely
OL,4,Cimportant' Troubles information sharing
OL,6,FSir Declan Morgan, chief commissioner
OL,7,Fof the Independent Commission on
OL,8,FReconciliation and Information
OL,9,FRecovery (ICRIR) ` which investigates
OL,10,FTroubles Crimes under the Labour
OL,11,FGovernment's reformed Legacy Act, has
OL,12,Fsaid the body does not have
OL,13,Finformation sharing arrangements with
OL,14,Fthe Irish authorities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
