OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772067788
OL,3,CHilary Benn to press Dublin on 'hugely
OL,4,Cimportant' Troubles information sharing
OL,6,F"There is no doubt that sharing of
OL,7,Finformation by the Irish authorities
OL,8,Fwill be hugely important for legacy
OL,9,Finvestigations and the Omagh bombing
OL,10,Finquiry.
OL,12,F"I greatly look forward to discussing
OL,13,Fthe Irish and UK legislation, and
OL,14,Fother issues of mutual interest, with
OL,15,FMinisters McEntee and O'Callaghan
OL,16,Flater today."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
