PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772067788
OL,3,CHilary Benn to press Dublin on 'hugely
OL,4,Cimportant' Troubles information sharing
OL,6,FThe ICRIR is already investigating
OL,7,Fmore killings than the Metropolitan
OL,8,Fpolice. It has more than 100 live
OL,9,Finvestigations, including into a
OL,10,Fnumber of unsolved IRA attacks on UK
OL,11,Fservice personnel such as the
OL,12,FGuildford pub bombings, the
OL,13,FWarrenpoint massacre and the M62 coach
OL,14,Fbombing.
OL,16,FLast year, Sir Declan said "it is
OL,17,Fessential" for victims and survivors
OL,18,Fto find out "what information Ireland
OL,19,Fholds in relation to what happened to
OL,20,Ftheir loved ones".
OL,26,@xD@\OUyD@JO]zD@MOU|D@QO]
